<refsect1>
<title>Description</title>
<para>
Normally, when the AnonRequirePassword directive is used, the
authentication is done using the password entry of the daemon
process. However under certain circumstances it may be required for the
authentication to be done using the login username & password instead.
</para>

</refsect1>

